{"type": "article", "id": 28410, "title": "模拟自然光的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-20T06:55:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 57, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021647310OMgLbBw78xsmkei.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>当你的台灯本身就能够模拟自然光的变化，你还需要用五花八门的滤镜来调节照片的颜色吗？来自德国的设计团队 <a href=\"https://heavn.io/en/\">Heavn</a> 最近推出了一款名为 Caffeine 的台灯，希望人们可以在自然光的节奏下进行办公。台灯提供了几种不同的照明模式，通过柱状灯管一端的按钮进行切换。室外模式下灯光会模仿一天内光照强度自动变化明暗，也可以根据需要切换成冷色或者暖色：前者的蓝色波长可以抑制睡眠，后者则会让人感到轻松舒适。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164729k8wQlMAXIPTVuUSF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.29142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164729dVvrOpMRmEkaXiC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021647304xFLNQMXKT7gzfOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702164730nmkXrP8yuULQo7pA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}